            "id": 80376,
            "contentType": "interactive",
            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Если мы не включаем оператор <code>return</code>, функция возвращает значение <code>None</code> вместо этого.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"age_label\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(age)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  label = \" /><text value=\"&quot;User age: &quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\" + age\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"result = age_label(\" /><text value=\"&quot;29&quot;\" class=\"string\" /><text value=\")\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(result)\" /></content><output><content><text value=\"None\" /></content></output></code></body></html>"
