            "images": [],
            "interactiveContent": "<!DOCTYPE html ><html><body><p>Вызови функцию <code>add_ten()</code> с каким-либо значением.</p><code version=\"2\" codelang=\"python\" name=\"script.py\" visible-if=\"always\"><content><text value=\"def\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" \" /><text value=\"add_ten\" class=\"title\" /><text value=\"(number)\" class=\"params\" /><text value=\":\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  total = \" /><text value=\"10\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\" + number\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"  \" /><text value=\"return\" class=\"keyword\" /><text value=\" total\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text type=\"break\" /><text value=\"print(add_ten(\" /><text value=\"20\" class=\"number\" /><text value=\"))\" /></content><interactions><interaction type=\"fillTheGap\" isDefault=\"true\"><options><option startIndex=\"65\" endIndex=\"72\" /><option startIndex=\"72\" endIndex=\"73\" /><option startIndex=\"73\" endIndex=\"75\" /><option startIndex=\"75\" endIndex=\"76\" /></options></interaction></interactions><output><content><text value=\"30\" /></content></output></code><p visible-if=\"wrong\">Обязательно выбери <code>add_ten</code>, затем <code>(</code>, а затем <code>20</code>, <code>)</code>.</p></body></html>"
